This sulfurous oil can cover one weapon, and takes 10 minutes to apply. The next creature to touch the weapon must resist its magic or become temporarily [[cursed]]. While cursed, the creature is unwilling to part with the weapon, and has [[disadvantage]] on attempts to use other weapons. The curse lasts for 5 minutes, or until [[magically removed|remove curse]].